Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.80,0:23:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,連我都開始緊張了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.13,0:23:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.21,0:23:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,請進請進,抱歉有點亂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.55,0:24:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那邊請坐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.25,0:24:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,芹澤,快去倒茶
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.13,0:24:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,倒倒…倒茶?
